These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, architect
2 different pets are kept: horse, cat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, golf
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, bike
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the architect is the owner of the horse##1
4. the engineer is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage    | iced-tea       | coffee  |
| Job         | engineer | architect |
| Pet         | cat        | horse     |
| Sport       | golf     | cricket  |
| Transport   | bus    | bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, cola
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, firefighter
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, train
1. the firefighter is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |       2       |
| Beverage    | tea  | cola        |
| Job         | firefighter | coach     |
| Pet         | dog  | hedgehog        |
| Sport       | ice-hockey  | parkour |
| Transport   | train      | quad-bike        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-3::.
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, peas
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, photographer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, metal
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, biathlon
1. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the paramedic##1
3. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |    2     |
| Food          | peas             | artichoke  |
| Hobby         | skydiving         | writing  |
| Job           | paramedic | photographer  |
| Music-Genre   | country         | metal      |
| Sport         | biathlon      | rugby |

