.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-4::.
There 2 different types of food: grapes, grapefruit
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, manager
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, disaster
There are 2 different nationalities: british, russian
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
2. the british is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the manager is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Food          | grapes    | grapefruit     |
| Job           | writer   | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | disaster     |
| Nationality   | british  | russian    |
| Transport     | skateboard | quad-bike       |

