.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, traveling
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, mystery
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, disco
2 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, rowing
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby         | photography     | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | sports   |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | indie |
| Pet           | rabbit         | snake     |
| Sport         | rowing  | cricket |

 